Game : Silver
Origin : USA - NTSC
Released : June 28th, 2000

Release Notes
Today we bring you a decent RPG for your Dreamcast. This one requires 
an 80 Minute CD, Don't try to overburn this one, Probably won't work. 

Game Info:
~~~~~~~~~~
Terror grips the land. The powerful and evil Sorcerer Silver has abducted the women of Jarrah for his treacherous purposes.

Take control as David, a simple hero on a quest to save his beloved and defeat the almighty Silver. But it won't be easy. In order to succeed you'll need to recruit allies, master swordplay, learn the art of magic, and venture through hostile worlds teeming with Silver's corrupt followers. 
